Subject: drm/nvd0/disp: ignore clock set if no pclk
Git-commit: dd62608bcc8a629c4c583fb50b90003fd5213516
Patch-mainline: v3.4-rc1

This happens somehow during init on a machine I have, and leads to a
divide-by-zero.

Lets avoid that...

